{
  "stem": "7358.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, especially when the war broke out between Germany and Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall, exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But everybody knew that there was a war, because refugees became to-- to come from-- from distant lands.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told us of terrible atrocities that the Germans were committing at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we really were very-- the town was-- I mean, as much as I can remember, we were very concerned at the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Eventually, the Russians made an agreement with the Germans, and they divided Poland in half.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Russians, in 1939, I believe in September, they, they came into our-- they occupied our part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we fell in under Russian domination.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So for all intents and purposes, we got two years' reprieve, until the point where the Germans subsequently declared war on Russia and occupied our area.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To-- to us, when the Russians came into our town, it was a very major change.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They immediately proclaimed that the proletarians, that the laborers, the workers, are everything, and all the other people are on the way down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they really resented the rich people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a campaign of eliminating the intelligensia and the-- and the well-to-do people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father was, unfortunately, also marked as being a well-to-do person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And therefore, he exploited workers along the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he-- and, and the documentations that were given to us, a number 11 was put into our passport, which indicated an undesirable person in the Russian society.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Other people of-- in our-- in our circle of friends were gradually being deported to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We would wake up in the morning, and we would hear that the Cohens disappeared, and the Feldmans disappeared during the night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And things were very tense for us, as sort of being in an upper class.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
